  "description": "Product Description:\n\nThis elegant lab-grown emerald ring features a classic four-prong setting crafted from high-quality S925 sterling silver, known for its hypoallergenic and tarnish-resistant properties. With a timeless three-stone design, this piece offers sophistication and durability for everyday elegance.\n\nThe centerpiece of this ring is a stunning 8x6mm, 1.44-carat emerald-cut lab-grown emerald, radiating a rich green hue that symbolizes harmony and renewal. Complementing the central stone are two additional emerald-cut side stones, adding 0.52 carats of brilliance to the design. Weighing 2.57 grams and available in U.S. sizes 5 to 7.5, this ring is lightweight yet sturdy. Please note that lab-grown colored gemstone rings ship within 3-15 days.\n\nKey Features:\n\nLab-Grown Emerald Center Stone: A vibrant 8x6mm, 1.44-carat emerald-cut stone, embodying beauty and sophistication.\n\nClassic Three-Stone Design: Enhanced by two emerald-cut side stones, totaling 0.52 carats, for a balanced and refined look.\n\nS925 Sterling Silver: Durable, hypoallergenic, and resistant to tarnish.\n\nPerfect Fit: Weighs 2.57 grams, available in U.S. ring sizes 5 to 7.5.\n\nShipping: Lab-grown colored gemstone rings have an estimated shipping time of 3-15 days.\n\nThis ring is an ideal choice for those who desire an elegant, timeless piece that radiates grace and charm.",
